localizations.tr.title: AMONG US SONG - NO MORE IMPOSTORS (Animation)
localizations.tr.description:
Among us song
Şarkı sözleri

Bu soğuk uzay gemisinde başka bir gün,
Küçük oğlum, yanımda.
Koridorlarda yürüyoruz
Görevlerin tamamlanması,
Ama uzaktan duyuyorum
En çok korktuğum şey!

Ceset rapor edildi,
maviyi öldürdüler
Bebeğimin favorisi
Arkadaşımız doğruydu.

Tartışma başlar, kim olabilir?
Bebek babamdan şüpheleniyorlar,
Anılara rağmen
o çok kolaylıkla dışarı atıldı.

Neden sahtekarlar var?
Neden utanmadan öldürülüyoruz?
Bebeğimi neden babasından aldı?
Ve belki annesinden?
Neden sabotaje yapmak zorundasın?

Ne olacağını merak etmeye başladım
Bebeğimin, eğer sonra ben olsaydım.
Ama devam etmeliyim, görevimi tamamlamalıyım
Ve başka bir trajediden kaçınmaya çalışın.

Aniden arkamda ayak sesleri duyuyorum.
Ne olabilirdi?
Acı vücudumu işgal ediyor
Kan odayı doldurur.
Sahtekar devam eder.

Korkma çocuğum
Şimdi bir ruh olarak
Senin için savaşırım
Hedefimize ulaşana kadar.
Hedefimize ulaşana kadar

Neden sahtekarlar var?
Neden utanmadan öldürülüyoruz?

Birisi vücudumu rapor ediyor
Tartışma başlıyor,
Minim ben de katılıyor.

Kimse bilmiyor
Kimin yaptığını kimse görmedi.
Utanmazca öldüren kişi.

Ama kalplerini takip ediyorlar
Ve sahtekar için oy verin,
Artık aramızda değil.


Beni desteklediğiniz için çok teşekkürler!
Seni seviyorum! ❤️

Hornstromp'un orijinal klibi.

Aramızda, Innersloth tarafından geliştirilen ve yayınlanan Amerikan yapımı bilim kurgu tabanlı bir cinayet gizem video oyunudur. Inc. 15 Haziran 2018'de IOS ve Android için, 18 Ağustos 2018'de PC için Steam'de ve 2 Kasım 2018'de Dajolg için piyasaya çıktı.

Her oyunda, oyuncu birkaç farklı ortamda yaşayan ve çalışan 4 ila 10 kişiden biridir. Bu mürettebat arkadaşlarından biri, asıl amacı herkesi öldürmek olan bir Sahtekar. Oyuncuların geri kalanı, sadece zarar görmeden kaçmaya çalışan normal ekibin bir parçasıdır. Bunu yapmak için, birkaç görevi tamamlamaları veya (daha iyisi) Sahtekar'ı bulmaları ve onları Survivor tarzında oylamaları gerekir. Başarılı olurlarsa Mürettebat kazanır. Impostor hepsini öldürmeyi başarırsa, oyuncu galip gelir. Bir Sahtekar ile 10 oyunculu bir oyunda, Sahtekar olma ihtimali% 10'dur.

Ücretsiz harita Skeld, 7 koridorla birbirine bağlanan 14 farklı odaya sahiptir. Herkes oyuna Kafeteryada başlar ve ev sahibinin ayarlarına ve ayrıca RNG'ye bağlı olarak, Mürettebat üyelerinin görevlerini tamamlamak için diğer odaların bir kısmını veya çoğunu ziyaret etmesi gerekir.

Sahtekarların belirli hedefleri gibi görevleri olmasa da, başkalarının güvenini kazanmanın bir yolu olarak belirli etkinlikleri "tamamlamayı" taklit edebilirler. Her kullanıcının bir acil durum toplantısı yapma veya bir ceset gördüğünde bunu herkese bildirme şansı vardır. Mobil sürüm için, tartışmalar yalnızca bu sınırlı süreli etkinlikler sırasında mümkündür.

Eğer bir Sahtekâr iseniz, asıl amacınız başkalarını Sahtekar olmadığınıza ikna etmek, Mürettebatın işi ise sizi tespit etmektir. En çok oyu alan kişinin oyundan elendiği bir oylama sistemi olduğu için kimin ne yaptığı pek de önemli değil. Bunun yerine, argümantasyon güçleriniz fark yaratan şeydir. İnsanları bir yöne ya da diğerine yönlendirmek için, durumunuzu olabildiğince ikna edici hale getirmeye hazırlıklı olmalısınız. Kısa bir zaman sınırı vardır, bu nedenle ya çok güçlü kanıtlar sunmanız ya da başkalarını peşinizden sürükleyecek inandırıcı bir anlatı oluşturmanız gerekir.

Sahtekar tarafından öldürüldüğünde, bir hayalet olursun. Başkalarıyla etkileşim kuramasanız veya tartışamasanız da, görevleri tamamlamalarına yardımcı olabilirsiniz.

Yayıncılar sohbetin ana iletişim biçimi olduğundan şikayet etti, bu nedenle birçok yayıncı sesli sohbet için uyumsuzluk kullandı.

localizations.hu.title: AMONG US SONG - NO MORE IMPOSTORS (Animation)
localizations.hu.description:
Among us Song
Dalszöveg

Még egy nap ezen a hideg űrhajón,
Kisfiam, mellettem.
Sétálunk a folyosón,
Feladatok elvégzése,
De a távolban hallom,
Amitől a legjobban félek!

A testület jelentette,
megölték a kéket,
A babám kedvence,
A barátunk igaz volt.

Megkezdődik a vita, ki lehet az?
Gondolják a babapapámat,
Az emlékek ellenére
annyi könnyedséggel kidobják.

Miért vannak csalók?
Miért gyilkolnak szégyentelenül?
Miért veszem el a babámat az apjától?
És talán az anyjától?
Miért kell szabotajozni?

Hagytam, hogy vajon mi lenne
A babámból, ha legközelebb én lennék.
De tovább kell folytatnom a feladatom,
És próbáljon elkerülni egy újabb tragédiát.

Hirtelen lépéseket hallok magam mögött.
Mi lehet az?
A fájdalom megszállja a testemet
Vér tölti be a szobát.
Az imádkozó folytatódik.

Ne félj a gyermekemtől,
Most mint lélek,
Nem bánom
Amíg el nem érjük a célunkat.
Amíg el nem érjük a célunkat

Miért vannak csalók?
Miért gyilkolnak szégyentelenül?

Valaki jelenti a testemet,
Megkezdődik a vita,
A mini me csatlakozik.

Senki sem tudja, ki az,
Senki sem látta, ki csinálta.
Aki szégyentelenül gyilkolt.

De követik a szívüket,
És szavazzon az imádkozóra,
Most már nincs köztünk.

Nagyon köszönöm, hogy támogattok!
Szeretlek! ❤️

Eredeti klip: Hornstromp.

Közöttünk van egy amerikai gyártmányú, tudományos-fantasztikus alapú gyilkossági misztérium-videojáték, amelyet Innersloth fejlesztett ki és tett közzé. Inc. IOS-ra és Android-ra jelent meg 2018. június 15-én, PC-re a Steamen 2018. augusztus 18-án és a Dajolg számára 2018. november 2-án. Közöttünk követi a legénységet, akit egy-egy impostor válogatott ki.

Minden játékban a játékos 4–10 él és dolgozik, különféle környezetekben. E stábtársak egyike az Impostor, akinek fő célja mindenki más megölése. A többi játékos a rendes legénység része, akik épségben próbálnak menekülni. Ehhez több feladatot kell végrehajtaniuk, vagy (még jobb) meg kell találniuk az Imposztort, és kiszavazni őket Survivor stílusban. Ha sikerrel járnak, a legénység nyer. Ha az Impostornak sikerül mindet megölnie, a játékos győz. Egy 10 fős játékban, egy Impostorral 10% esély van arra, hogy Impostor legyél.

A Skeld ingyenes térképen 14 különböző szoba található, amelyeket 7 folyosó köt össze. Mindenki a Cafeteria-ban kezdi a játékot, és a házigazda beállításaitól, valamint az RNG-től függően a legénység tagjainak a feladatok elvégzéséhez meg kell látogatniuk a többi helyiség egyikét vagy a legtöbbet.

Míg az imposzoroknak nem konkrét feladataik vannak, akkor hamisíthatják bizonyos tevékenységek „befejezését”, hogy megszerezzék mindenki más bizalmát. Minden felhasználónak lehetősége van sürgősségi értekezletet összehívni, vagy holttest láttán jelenteni mindenkinek. A mobil kiadás esetében a megbeszélések csak ezekben az időkorlátos eseményekben lehetségesek.

Ha Ön rendező, akkor az a fő célja, hogy meggyőzze másokat arról, hogy nem Ön az Imposzor, míg a személyzet feladata az, hogy kiszúrjon. Mivel ez egy olyan szavazási rendszer, ahol a legtöbb szavazatot elért személy kiesik a játékból, teljesen mindegy, ki mit csinál. Ehelyett az érvelési képességei jelentenek változást. Ahhoz, hogy az embereket egyik vagy másik irányba ingassa, fel kell készülnie arra, hogy ügyét a lehető legmeggyőzőbbé tegye. Rövid időkorlát van, ezért vagy nagyon erős bizonyítékot kell bemutatnia, vagy egy hihető elbeszéléssel kell előállnia, amely másokat levon a nyomáról.

Amikor az Impostor megöl, szellem leszel. Noha nem léphet kapcsolatba másokkal, és nem tud megbeszélni másokkal, segíthet nekik a feladatok elvégzésében.

A közvetítők panaszkodtak arra, hogy a csevegés a kommunikáció fő formája, ezért sok közvetítő diszkriminációt alkalmazott a hangos csevegéshez.

snippet.title: Apex Legends Champion Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Make your name with the Champion Edition, packed full of character unlocks and exclusive items to get you started right. http://x.ea.com/65702

Ready to become an Apex Champion? You could be, with all the incredible items stuffed into the Champion Edition. You’ll get every Legend up to Season 7, plus over $100 worth of exclusive cosmetics, including Legendary character and weapon skins and a Legendary gun charm, along with a thousand Apex Coins. Play who you want, dress how you want, and show those other Legends there’s a new champ in town. 

Starting Season 7, you can find the Champion Edition on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and Origin on PC or get a download card at your favorite retailer soon for $39.99. Here’s everything you’ll find inside:

The Champion Edition
- 9 character unlocks (all Legends up to Season 7):
Caustic, Mirage, Octane, Wattson, Crypto, Revenant, Loba, Rampart, and the Season 7 Legend 
- 7 Exclusive Legendary items:
- “Risen Queen” Wraith skin
- “Forged Knight” Revenant skin
- “Hallowed Spirit” Crypto skin
- “Curse of the Awaken” Triple Take skin
- “Slayer’s Lancer” Flatline skin
- “Jaded Myth” Sentinel skin
- "Emperor Nessy XIV" Gun Charm
- 1,000 Apex Coins

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC. 

Learn more about Apex Legends Season 6 – Boosted: http://x.ea.com/64060
 
Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

#PlayApex #ApexSeason6 #ChampionEdition #ApexLegends

localizations.da.title: Apex Legends Champion Edition-trailer
localizations.da.description:
Slå dit navn fast med Champion Edition, der er proppet med ting, du kan låse op til din figur, samt eksklusive genstande, der vil få dig godt i gang. http://x.ea.com/65702

Er du klar til at blive Apex-mester? Det kan du blive med alle de fantastiske genstande, som Champion Edition indeholder. Du får alle legender op til sæson 7 samt eksklusive pyntegenstande til en værdi af mere end 100 $, inklusive legendariske karakter- og våbenskins samt et legendarisk våbensmykke sammen med 1000 Apex-mønter. Spil, som du vil, klæd dig, som du vil, og vis de andre legender, at der er en ny mester i arenaen. 

Med sæson 7 kan du finde Champion Edition på Xbox One, PlayStation 4 og Origin til pc eller som download-kort hos din foretrukne forhandler for 39,99 $. Her er en oversigt over indholdet:

Champion Edition
●        9 oplåste legender (alle legender frem til sæson 7):
○        Caustic, Mirage, Octane, Wattson, Crypto, Revenant, Loba, Rampart og sæson 7-legenden

○    Curse of the Awaken-utseende för Triple Take
○    Slayer's Lancer-utseende för Flatline

localizations.pl.description:
Zdobądź sławę z Edycją Mistrzowską, wypełnioną po brzegi odblokowanymi postaciami i wyjątkowymi przedmiotami, które zapewnią ci należyty start w grze. http://x.ea.com/65702

Graj kim chcesz, ubieraj się jak chcesz i pokaż reszcie legend, że w mieście pojawił się nowy czempion. 

Od sezonu 7. znajdziesz Edycję Mistrzowską do kupienia na platformach Xbox One, PlayStation 4 i Origin na PC. Za 39,99 $ możesz też kupić w lokalnym sklepie kod do pobrania**. Oto wszystko, co znajdziesz w pakiecie:

localizations.ru.description:
Заявите о себе с помощью издания чемпиона, которое включает кучу персонажей и эксклюзивных предметов. http://x.ea.com/65702

Готовы стать чемпионом Apex? Это вполне возможно. А предметы из издания чемпиона помогут вам заявить о себе. Вы получите всех легенд, выпущенных до 7-го сезона, а также эксклюзивные предметы внешнего вида на сумму более 100 $, включая легендарные облики и раскраски и легендарный талисман для оружия, а также 1000 монет Apex. Играйте за кого хотите, одевайтесь, как хотите, и покажите другим легендам, что к ним пожаловал новый чемпион. 

Начиная с 7-го сезона, издание чемпиона будет доступно на Xbox One, PlayStation 4 и в Origin для ПК, а скоро появится и на картах загрузки в вашем любимом розничном магазине за 39,99 $. Вот что вы в нем найдете:

Издание чемпиона

○        Каустик, Мираж, Октейн, Ваттсон, Крипто, Ревенант, Лоба, Рампарт и легенда сезона 7 
●        7 эксклюзивных легендарных предметов:
○        Облик Рэйф «Восставшая королева»
○        Облик Ревенанта «Кованый рыцарь»
○        Облик Крипто «Священный дух»
○        Раскраска для «Тройного эффекта» «Проклятие пробуждения»

○        Раскраска для «Стража» «Устаревший миф»

●        1000 монет Apex

Apex Legends™ — бесплатная игра в жанре «королевская битва», где легендарные персонажи сражаются за славу и богатства на дальних рубежах Фронтира. Играйте бесплатно на Xbox One, PS4 и в Origin для ПК.

localizations.ja.description:
チャンピオンエディションで君の名を轟かせよう。全キャラクターがアンロックされ、限定アイテムを今すぐ装備してバトルに参戦可能だ。http://x.ea.com/65702

Apexチャンピオンを目指そう！チャンピオンエディションに収録される豪華アイテムを手にすれば、チャンピオンも夢ではない。シーズン7までの全レジェンドがアンロック。加えて、100ドル相当の限定装飾アイテムも収録される。レジェンダリーのキャラクタースキンや武器スキン、レジェンダリーガンチャーム、そして1000 Apexコインも手に入る。好きなキャラクターを好きなアイテムで着飾り、他のレジェンドたちに新たなチャンピオンの到来を見せつけてやろう。

シーズン7開始と同時にXbox One、PlayStation®4、Origin（PC）版のチャンピオンエディションをご用意。販売店ではダウンロードカードもお買い求めいただけます。お値段は$39.99です。収録内容:

チャンピオンエディション
●        9人のキャラクターをアンロック（シーズン7までの全キャラクター）:
○        コースティック、ミラージュ、オクタン、ワットソン、クリプト、レヴナント、ローバ、ランパート、シーズン7のレジェンド
●        限定レジェンダリーアイテム7種:
○        レイス用スキン「昇日の女王」
○        レヴナント用スキン「人造の騎士」
○        クリプト用スキン「神聖なる魂」
○        トリプルテイク用スキン「覚醒の呪い」
○        フラットライン用スキン「スレイヤーズランサー」
○        センチネル用スキン「退屈な神話」
○        ガンチャーム「皇帝ネッシーXIV」
●        1,000 Apexコイン

「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は、伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う、基本プレイ無料のバトルロイヤル作品。Xbox One、PS4、Origin（PC）で今すぐ無料プレイ。

snippet.title: Boris Johnson and Rishi Sunak lay out plans for new lockdown
snippet.description:
The Prime Minister has announced a new three-tier strategy for local lockdowns in an address to the nation.

The three-tier system will see different parts of England placed in different categories dependent on rates of infection, with areas in the highest level expected to face the toughest restrictions.

Chancellor Rishi Sunak also set out the Government's three part plan to protect jobs and businesses through the winter.

The job support scheme will protect jobs whether your business is open or closed, Mr Sunak says.

"If you're business can open safely, but with reduced or uncertain demand the Government will directly subsidise people's wages over the winter," he adds. 

Subscribe to The Telegraph on YouTube ► https://bit.ly/3idrdLH

Get the latest headlines: https://www.telegraph.co.uk/

Telegraph.co.uk and YouTube.com/TelegraphTV are websites of The Telegraph, the UK's best-selling quality daily newspaper providing news and analysis on UK and world events, business, sport, lifestyle and culture.

snippet.title: Is Herd Immunity The Way To End The Covid Crisis? | This Morning
snippet.description:
Last night Boris Johnson announced a new three-tier alert system in England to try to stop the spread of coronavirus. The Liverpool City Region has been placed into the ‘Very High’ category, meaning pubs and bars must close and people cannot meet with anybody outside their household or support bubble. We’re joined by Professor David Livermore, one of 2,500 academics who has signed a declaration urging world leaders to halt “harmful” Covid restrictions in favour of pursuing a strategy of herd immunity. We’re also joined by Dr Simon Clarke, from the University of Reading, who disagrees and thinks lockdowns are the only option to control the spread.
Broadcast on 13/10/20

snippet.title: Watch Three New Crew Members Launch to the International Space Station
snippet.description:
Tune in LIVE as three space travelers launch to the International Space Station on Wednesday, Oct. 14, at 1:45 a.m. EDT. 

Astronaut Kate Rubins of NASA, and Sergey Ryzhikov and Sergey Kud-Sverchkov of the Russian space agency Roscosmos will lift off aboard the Soyuz MS-17 spacecraft for a two-orbit, three-hour journey to dock to the orbiting laboratory. Live coverage of the launch begins at 12:45 a.m. EDT.

This is the second trip to space for both Rubins and Ryzhikov, and the first for Kud-Sverchkov. During their six-month mission, they will welcome SpaceX Crew-1 astronauts Mike Hopkins, Victor Glover and Shannon Walker of NASA, and Soichi Noguchi of JAXA (Japan Aerospace Exploration Agency).

snippet.title: What Happened to Simon?
snippet.description:
I’ve taken a few months off of being on camera.  I’ve seen many comments from people asking what happened to me, and I understand.  I kinda left without any word.  I’m sorry for that.  Let me tell you what’s been going on in my life. 

For those of you that are frustrated by my lack of responding to other burning questions that you might have, please don’t let that frustration turn into anger towards me.  It’s not that I’m not addressing speculations out of a disrespect towards you.  If that’s your first guess, I’m telling you it’s the wrong guess: there are other reasons.  There are some parts of my private life that I just don’t feel comfortable talking about yet.  

I made this video because I did see that many were concerned about me.  I wanted to make this video for them.  And I wanted to just let people know that, even though this is a VERY huge transition in my life, I’m actually doing well in the face of it.  I am doing better than I thought I would.  I hope that’s the message people can walk away with, and not let their frustration out of curiosity taint that message.  I’ll talk about other parts of my life only when I’m comfortable talking about them, and not a second before that, even under a deluge of pressure from others.  I’m asking you: please be kind.

snippet.localized.title: What Happened to Simon?
snippet.localized.description:
I’ve taken a few months off of being on camera.  I’ve seen many comments from people asking what happened to me, and I understand.  I kinda left without any word.  I’m sorry for that.  Let me tell you what’s been going on in my life. 

For those of you that are frustrated by my lack of responding to other burning questions that you might have, please don’t let that frustration turn into anger towards me.  It’s not that I’m not addressing speculations out of a disrespect towards you.  If that’s your first guess, I’m telling you it’s the wrong guess: there are other reasons.  There are some parts of my private life that I just don’t feel comfortable talking about yet.  

I made this video because I did see that many were concerned about me.  I wanted to make this video for them.  And I wanted to just let people know that, even though this is a VERY huge transition in my life, I’m actually doing well in the face of it.  I am doing better than I thought I would.  I hope that’s the message people can walk away with, and not let their frustration out of curiosity taint that message.  I’ll talk about other parts of my life only when I’m comfortable talking about them, and not a second before that, even under a deluge of pressure from others.  I’m asking you: please be kind.

snippet.title: BLACKPINK – ‘Lovesick Girls’ M/V
snippet.description:
BLACKPINK – ‘Lovesick Girls’

영원한 밤
창문 없는 방에 우릴 가둔 love
What can we say
매번 아파도 외치는 love

다치고 망가져도 나
뭘 믿고 버티는 거야
어차피 떠나면 상처투성인 채로 미워하게 될걸
끝장을 보기 전 끝낼 순 없어
이 아픔을 기다린 것처럼

아마 다 잠깐 일지도 몰라
우린 무얼 찾아서 헤매는 걸까

But I don’t care I’ll do it over and over
내 세상 속엔 너만 있으면 돼

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔 없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

But we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone 
But why we still looking for love

No love letters, no x and o’s
No love never, my exes know
No diamond rings, that set in stone
To the left, better left alone

Didn’t wanna be a princess, I’m priceless
A prince not even on my list
Love is a drug that I quit
No doctor could help when I’m lovesick

아마 다 잠깐 일지도 몰라
우린 무얼 찾아서 헤매는 걸까

불안한 내 눈빛 속에 널 담아
아프더라도 너만 있으면 돼

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼 순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔 없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

But we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone 
But why we still looking for love

사랑은 slippin’ and fallin’
사랑은 killin’ your darlin’
아프다 아물면 또 찾아오는 이 겁 없는 떨림

들리지 않아 what you say
이 아픔이 난 행복해
나를 불쌍해 하는 네가 내 눈엔 더 불쌍해

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼 순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

Lovesick girls 
모두 결국 떠나가고
Lovesick girls
내 눈물이 무뎌져도
Lovesick girls
아프고 또 아파도
Lovesick girls
But we’re still looking for love

snippet.title: The life of purple rice, pumpkins, and … peanuts紫米南瓜的一生…，还有花生丨Liziqi Channel
snippet.description:
Please  subscribe to 【李子柒 Liziqi 】Liziqi Channel on YouTube if you like my videos: https://goo.gl/nkjpSx 
Sow in spring to grow in summer, harvest in autumn for storage in winter.
And Autumn Equinox has given way to Cold Dew now.
We have finished reaping the corn, grain, pumpkins, and peanuts,
ready to await the frost and snow in winter.
For the past Mid-Autumn Day, my cousin and cousin-in-law came back to spend the festival with granny.
Chitter-chatter, lively and jolly--that’s how festivals should be!
春生夏长，秋收冬藏。
秋分已去寒露来。
忙完玉米 谷子 南瓜 花生的收获存储之后
就该等着霜雪天的到来，
中秋，表姐和表姐夫两口子来陪奶奶过节。
吵吵闹闹的，倒也过了这个秋！

We have finished reaping the corn, grain, pumpkins, and peanuts,
ready to await the frost and snow in winter.
For the past Mid-Autumn Day, my cousin and cousin-in-law came back to spend the festival with granny.
Chitter-chatter, lively and jolly--that’s how festivals should be!
春生夏长，秋收冬藏。
秋分已去寒露来。
忙完玉米 谷子 南瓜 花生的收获存储之后
就该等着霜雪天的到来，
中秋，表姐和表姐夫两口子来陪奶奶过节。
吵吵闹闹的，倒也过了这个秋！

snippet.title: Rafael Nadal vs Novak Djokovic - Final Highlights I Roland-Garros 2020
snippet.description:
Rafael Nadal vs Novak Djokovic - Final Highlights I Roland-Garros 2020. Watch the best moments of the final between Rafael Nadal and Novak Djokovic. The Spanish player won in three sets 6/0 6/2 7/5 and claimed his 13th Roland-Garros, his 20th Grand Slam. It's his 100th victory in Roland-Garros.
These highlights were brought to you by Emirates.

snippet.title: I Tested Clickbait DIY Soap "Hacks"
snippet.description:
Hello friends! So, after a long break from testing out & reviewing clickbait hack videos (I think the photo and video hacks broke me), we decided to make a comeback into the genre by testing out these viral clickbait soap hacks that lots of hackers seem to love making - from Blossom to 5-Minute Crafts to Craft Factory and back. And you know me, I can't resist me some nice soap :). We tried a cloud soap hack, a gummy bear soap hack, and a cinnamon roll soap hack, and shenanigans ensued. 

What do you guys think of these soap hacks??

Also, a heads up - though we mention it in the video - cinnamon can be dangerous to use on your skin and ivory soap can release fumes when being microwaved (I guess that's why it smelled so bad), so definitely be careful if you take on any of these soap art "hacks" yourself!!

You can check out Katie from Royalty Soap's video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-UDhSQYVWss
You can check out the Blossom video that contains our hacks here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4I1tMz-VMtg
And you can check out Jenna's soap hand video here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fo3HwJNgi9M

This video is NOT sponsored!!

Safiya's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/safiyany/

MUSIC
Via AudioNetwork

snippet.title: Apple's entire iPhone 12 event in exactly 12 minutes (supercut)
snippet.description:

You're watching CNET's supercut, an edited recap of the event, in 12 minutes, so you don't have to watch the whole hour-long event, just every product that was announced, back-to-back. For all this and more, be sure to subscribe for continued iPhone 12 news.

snippet.title: Can Anwar Ibrahim Become Malaysia's Prime Minister?
snippet.description: Oct.12 -- James Chin, professor of Asian studies at the University of Tasmania, look at the political turmoil in Malaysia. Opposition leader Anwar Ibrahim arrived at the palace to meet the king on Tuesday in a bid to prove he’s got the numbers to form a new government, even as the current ruling bloc says the move will fail. Chin speaks on "Bloomberg Markets: Asia."

snippet.title: 黃鴻升 Alien Huang 柯有倫 Alan Kuo 竇智孔 Bobby Dou 【扛得住 Carry On】Official Music Video
snippet.description:
【ROCK HDMV】
歡迎訂閱滾石唱片YouTube官方頻道 → http://bit.ly/RockRecords
#黃鴻升 #柯有倫 #竇智孔  《#扛得住》MV

Alien留給地球的最後一首友情歌
願大家一起將正能量傳出去

Alien黃鴻升「Plan B 專輯」第5首單曲
《扛得住》
黃鴻升 X 柯有倫 X 竇智孔
三位好友合唱
為後疫情時代的我們加油打氣
兄弟陪你一定可以扛得住

ALIEN黃鴻升2020專輯「Plan B」，從2019年開始籌備製作，這張專輯從最開始的A&R到專輯概念、企劃文案、拍攝ＭＶ，黃鴻升不假手他人，全部自己一手包辦，經紀人曾經擔心他手上工作太多太忙，在他寫歌詞卡關的時候，跟他說要不要乾脆找人寫詞，他思考了幾秒，肯定地說，他可以的，他自己來！

2019年6月陸續推出《蒸發》、《人生定番》、《Plan B》，時隔多月，在2020年6月再推出《我不是空笑夢》，在忙碌於主持節目、廣告代言、戲劇之外，黃鴻升對於歌手身份，已不想要只是做一個被公司規劃好的「歌手」，而是希望透過自己親手創作歌詞、寫歌曲介紹文案、拍攝ＭＶ，為自己的音樂找定位，為自己想唱的歌創造生命。

這首《扛得住》，預定在2020年9月底上架，在9月13日釋出歌名與三人的宣傳照，只是，來不及讓大家讀到他為這首歌寫的介紹文字。
所以，延續「Plan B」的精神，催生這首歌的柯有倫，以及共同合唱的竇智孔，各自為好友黃鴻升、為三人合唱的這首歌，寫下一段話，希望能夠真切傳達，關於這首歌的誕生、靈感與精神。

Alan柯有倫：
這首歌的誕生，最大的原因，其實是因爲今年疫情的關係，看到大家生活上面都遇到一些比較大的困苦，所以想要鼓勵大家，在這段時間一定要扛得住。

我們有個高爾夫球群組，前一陣子三個人常一起去高爾夫球練習場練球，因爲我們三個都希望，從今年開始，即使再忙，我們三個人都可以保持每一個月一定要下場打一場高爾夫球。
有一天，因爲這首歌寫出來，我就傳到群組裡面給他們聽，我說有沒有機會跟兩位兄弟一起唱這首歌。當然，他們兩個一聽完之後，立刻答應。
後來，我們去錄音室錄完這首歌的時候，鴻升跟我說，他希望可以把這首歌放在他的全新專輯，我跟竇哥聽了之後，當然也是一口答應。

這首歌詞曲創作的靈感，就像當年的《笨小孩》，我一直希望可以做一首是像當年的笨小孩，有三個兄弟，用一首曲子表達一種正面的力量。
我們三個人的想法應該都是一樣的，就是希望在生命裏面很簡單，然後可以做一件事情，是讓我們三個人都覺得是很正面，然後很快樂的。
在這個打拼的路上，我們三個兄弟互相都看到彼此的辛苦，也看到彼此的堅持與執着。希望能用這種心境，去鼓勵所有不管是遇到困難、或者是遇到挫折的人。

想跟鴻升說的就是，這一趟太短了，下輩子我們再做朋友、我們再做兄弟，有你在身邊一起並肩作戰，是我這一輩子最驕傲最光榮的事。

竇智孔：
9月18日.晚上18:42分
在收到滾石發來的信息後，
我想這是你搞的鬼吧！
我崩潰了。
你..太賤了....
我會在我的隱形筆記本裡註記的。
然後，
我回頭翻著簡訊，
我找到了我們兄弟情開始的地方。
我承認我不是一個好相處的人。
但你的舉動讓我決定把牆全打開了。
簡訊裡
我：我們外景提來賓，不知道你會不會願意來幫忙。
你：只要你需要我的，我就盡全力幫忙，ok!（你就是這麼可愛）
我想緣分就是這麼簡單
然後，我們完成了一些回憶，
當然我們還有很多約好的計畫……

沒事，兄弟，再見。
兄弟我扛得住！
我們保持聯絡⋯。

⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯

『無論是逼不得已，或是因為是退卻而放棄、
無論如何，儘管緊緊擁抱遺憾，時間仍舊不可逆。
時針分針秒針，前進的頻率不同， 方向卻總是一致。
時針不會為了你而開始逆轉，但你可以順著時間的流，釐清造成的不甘的源頭，
毫無懸念的繼續順時針前行。』

—截自Alien黃鴻升，2019/11/28 寫於「Plan B」專輯概念

計劃趕不上變化、時間也無法倒轉，
面對遺憾和困難，請讓 扛得住 成為定番。

這是他留給地球的最後一首友情歌，只要有音樂陪伴，相信大家一定扛得住；願每個人都永遠記得鴻升帶來的美好，一起將他的正能量傳遞出去。

黃鴻升 柯有倫 竇智孔《扛得住》♫ https://RockRecordsCo.lnk.to/CarryOn

扛得住 Carry On
演唱 Performed by：黃鴻升 Alien Huang / 柯有倫 Alan Kuo / 竇智孔 Bobby Dou
作曲 Composer：王君蒲 Apollo Wang
作詞 Lyricist：王君蒲 Apollo Wang

(黃)

snippet.localized.title: 黃鴻升 Alien Huang 柯有倫 Alan Kuo 竇智孔 Bobby Dou 【扛得住 Carry On】Official Music Video
snippet.localized.description:
【ROCK HDMV】
歡迎訂閱滾石唱片YouTube官方頻道 → http://bit.ly/RockRecords
#黃鴻升 #柯有倫 #竇智孔  《#扛得住》MV

Alien留給地球的最後一首友情歌
願大家一起將正能量傳出去

Alien黃鴻升「Plan B 專輯」第5首單曲
《扛得住》
黃鴻升 X 柯有倫 X 竇智孔
三位好友合唱
為後疫情時代的我們加油打氣
兄弟陪你一定可以扛得住

ALIEN黃鴻升2020專輯「Plan B」，從2019年開始籌備製作，這張專輯從最開始的A&R到專輯概念、企劃文案、拍攝ＭＶ，黃鴻升不假手他人，全部自己一手包辦，經紀人曾經擔心他手上工作太多太忙，在他寫歌詞卡關的時候，跟他說要不要乾脆找人寫詞，他思考了幾秒，肯定地說，他可以的，他自己來！

2019年6月陸續推出《蒸發》、《人生定番》、《Plan B》，時隔多月，在2020年6月再推出《我不是空笑夢》，在忙碌於主持節目、廣告代言、戲劇之外，黃鴻升對於歌手身份，已不想要只是做一個被公司規劃好的「歌手」，而是希望透過自己親手創作歌詞、寫歌曲介紹文案、拍攝ＭＶ，為自己的音樂找定位，為自己想唱的歌創造生命。

這首《扛得住》，預定在2020年9月底上架，在9月13日釋出歌名與三人的宣傳照，只是，來不及讓大家讀到他為這首歌寫的介紹文字。
所以，延續「Plan B」的精神，催生這首歌的柯有倫，以及共同合唱的竇智孔，各自為好友黃鴻升、為三人合唱的這首歌，寫下一段話，希望能夠真切傳達，關於這首歌的誕生、靈感與精神。

Alan柯有倫：
這首歌的誕生，最大的原因，其實是因爲今年疫情的關係，看到大家生活上面都遇到一些比較大的困苦，所以想要鼓勵大家，在這段時間一定要扛得住。

我們有個高爾夫球群組，前一陣子三個人常一起去高爾夫球練習場練球，因爲我們三個都希望，從今年開始，即使再忙，我們三個人都可以保持每一個月一定要下場打一場高爾夫球。
有一天，因爲這首歌寫出來，我就傳到群組裡面給他們聽，我說有沒有機會跟兩位兄弟一起唱這首歌。當然，他們兩個一聽完之後，立刻答應。
後來，我們去錄音室錄完這首歌的時候，鴻升跟我說，他希望可以把這首歌放在他的全新專輯，我跟竇哥聽了之後，當然也是一口答應。

這首歌詞曲創作的靈感，就像當年的《笨小孩》，我一直希望可以做一首是像當年的笨小孩，有三個兄弟，用一首曲子表達一種正面的力量。
我們三個人的想法應該都是一樣的，就是希望在生命裏面很簡單，然後可以做一件事情，是讓我們三個人都覺得是很正面，然後很快樂的。
在這個打拼的路上，我們三個兄弟互相都看到彼此的辛苦，也看到彼此的堅持與執着。希望能用這種心境，去鼓勵所有不管是遇到困難、或者是遇到挫折的人。

想跟鴻升說的就是，這一趟太短了，下輩子我們再做朋友、我們再做兄弟，有你在身邊一起並肩作戰，是我這一輩子最驕傲最光榮的事。

竇智孔：
9月18日.晚上18:42分
在收到滾石發來的信息後，
我想這是你搞的鬼吧！
我崩潰了。
你..太賤了....
我會在我的隱形筆記本裡註記的。
然後，
我回頭翻著簡訊，
我找到了我們兄弟情開始的地方。
我承認我不是一個好相處的人。
但你的舉動讓我決定把牆全打開了。
簡訊裡
我：我們外景提來賓，不知道你會不會願意來幫忙。
你：只要你需要我的，我就盡全力幫忙，ok!（你就是這麼可愛）
我想緣分就是這麼簡單
然後，我們完成了一些回憶，
當然我們還有很多約好的計畫……

沒事，兄弟，再見。
兄弟我扛得住！
我們保持聯絡⋯。

⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯

『無論是逼不得已，或是因為是退卻而放棄、
無論如何，儘管緊緊擁抱遺憾，時間仍舊不可逆。
時針分針秒針，前進的頻率不同， 方向卻總是一致。
時針不會為了你而開始逆轉，但你可以順著時間的流，釐清造成的不甘的源頭，
毫無懸念的繼續順時針前行。』

—截自Alien黃鴻升，2019/11/28 寫於「Plan B」專輯概念

計劃趕不上變化、時間也無法倒轉，
面對遺憾和困難，請讓 扛得住 成為定番。

這是他留給地球的最後一首友情歌，只要有音樂陪伴，相信大家一定扛得住；願每個人都永遠記得鴻升帶來的美好，一起將他的正能量傳遞出去。

snippet.title: Could Anwar Ibrahim be Malaysia's next prime minister? | Inside Story
snippet.description:
He's been on the verge of leading Malaysia for decades.
Now, opposition leader Anwar Ibrahim is again trying to grab the post of prime minister.
He says he's presented the king with evidence he has the required majority in parliament to unseat Muhyiddin Yassin.
Muhyiddin has only a two-seat majority and is struggling to maintain support.
The palace says Anwar has told the Monarch how many lawmakers backed him.
Anwar has urged Malaysians to be patient and give the king space to review his bid.
So, could he finally grab power?
And what would it mean for Malaysia?

Tricia Yeoh, CEO of  the Institute for Democracy and Economic Affairs.
Ibrahim Suffian, Executive Director of the Merdeka Centre, a public opinion research organisation.
Bridget Welsh, Senior Research Associate in the Centre for East Asia Democratic Studies at the National Taiwan University.

And connect accessories in a whole new way with MagSafe. iPhone 12 Pro, the most powerful iPhone ever.

snippet.title: I Tested Clickbait DIY Soap "Hacks"
snippet.description:
Hello friends! So, after a long break from testing out & reviewing clickbait hack videos (I think the photo and video hacks broke me), we decided to make a comeback into the genre by testing out these viral clickbait soap hacks that lots of hackers seem to love making - from Blossom to 5-Minute Crafts to Craft Factory and back. And you know me, I can't resist me some nice soap :). We tried a cloud soap hack, a gummy bear soap hack, and a cinnamon roll soap hack, and shenanigans ensued. 

What do you guys think of these soap hacks??

Also, a heads up - though we mention it in the video - cinnamon can be dangerous to use on your skin and ivory soap can release fumes when being microwaved (I guess that's why it smelled so bad), so definitely be careful if you take on any of these soap art "hacks" yourself!!

You can check out Katie from Royalty Soap's video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-UDhSQYVWss
You can check out the Blossom video that contains our hacks here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4I1tMz-VMtg
And you can check out Jenna's soap hand video here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fo3HwJNgi9M

This video is NOT sponsored!!

Safiya's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/safiyany/

MUSIC
Via AudioNetwork

snippet.title: Among Us But Its A Reality Show 2

🎬BEHIND THE SCENES: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UEUEy3RioYk

There are two imposters among us. After lots of band-aids and medbay visits, our friends are back and better than ever, have once again found themselves in the dark and lonely confines of space with nothing but their spaceship and crewmates. Our group has to figure out who on the ship are murderers, while making sure they are doing their tasks so that their spaceship doesn't continue to barrel roll. Is red sus or is blue? snippet.title: BLACKPINK – ‘Lovesick Girls’ M/V
snippet.description:
BLACKPINK – ‘Lovesick Girls’

영원한 밤
창문 없는 방에 우릴 가둔 love
What can we say
매번 아파도 외치는 love

다치고 망가져도 나
뭘 믿고 버티는 거야
어차피 떠나면 상처투성인 채로 미워하게 될걸
끝장을 보기 전 끝낼 순 없어
이 아픔을 기다린 것처럼

아마 다 잠깐 일지도 몰라
우린 무얼 찾아서 헤매는 걸까

But I don’t care I’ll do it over and over
내 세상 속엔 너만 있으면 돼

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔 없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

But we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone 
But why we still looking for love

No love letters, no x and o’s
No love never, my exes know
No diamond rings, that set in stone
To the left, better left alone

Didn’t wanna be a princess, I’m priceless
A prince not even on my list
Love is a drug that I quit
No doctor could help when I’m lovesick

아마 다 잠깐 일지도 몰라
우린 무얼 찾아서 헤매는 걸까

불안한 내 눈빛 속에 널 담아
아프더라도 너만 있으면 돼

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼 순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔 없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

But we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone 
But why we still looking for love

사랑은 slippin’ and fallin’
사랑은 killin’ your darlin’
아프다 아물면 또 찾아오는 이 겁 없는 떨림

들리지 않아 what you say
이 아픔이 난 행복해
나를 불쌍해 하는 네가 내 눈엔 더 불쌍해

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼 순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

Lovesick girls 
모두 결국 떠나가고
Lovesick girls
내 눈물이 무뎌져도
Lovesick girls
아프고 또 아파도
Lovesick girls
But we’re still looking for love

Available on @ https://smarturl.it/BLACKPINKTHEALBUM  
Official BLACKPINK Merchandise: http://smarturl.it/BLACKPINKShop/   

More about BLACKPINK @
http://www.blackpinkofficial.com/
http://www.facebook.com/BLACKPINKOFFICIAL
http://www.youtube.com/BLACKPINKOFFICIAL
http://www.instagram.com/BLACKPINKOFFICIAL
https://twitter.com/BLACKPINK

snippet.title: Yaar Jigree Kasooti Degree Season 2 | Episode 3 – REMAND | Latest Punjabi Web Series 2020
snippet.description:
After reuniting with Roop, Jass and Ekam have finally found some peace in their life. Now with new information about Anmol and Lucky, the trio has to find a way to bring their friends back. Watch the 3rd Episode of Yaar Jigri Kasuti Degree Season 2 - Presented by "Free Fire".  And don’t miss the 4th Episode which is all set to premiere on 17th October at 5:00 pm only on Troll Punjabi.

Download “Garena Free Fire” the Best survival Battle Royale on mobile: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dts.freefireth&hl=en_US

snippet.title: Meet iPhone 12 — Apple
snippet.description:
Hello 5G. A14 Bionic, the fastest smartphone chip ever. Night mode on all cameras. Super Retina XDR display. The first camera ever to record in Dolby Vision. Ceramic Shield that’s tougher than any other smartphone glass. A whole new way to connect accessories with MagSafe. And the world’s smallest 5G phone, iPhone 12 mini.

Learn more: http://apple.com/iphone-12
 
“Eat Them Apples” by Suzi Wu http://apple.co/EatThemApples

iPhone 12 mini has not been authorized as required by the rules of the Federal Communications Commission. This device is not, and may not be, offered for sale or lease, or sold or leased, until authorization is obtained.

snippet.title: Cape York | FLOODED 4WDs & the world’s best campsites | Budget build HiLux takes on the rest!
snippet.description:
Shauno & Jocko are back to take on the Old Telegraph Track in Cape York! Is there ANY better place to run in the 30?! Driving some of the best 4WD tracks in Australia the Dirty 30 and Pony Lux tackle the Tele Track, Gunshot Creek, Nolan's Brook, Palm Creek, Cockatoo Creek, Sam's Creek, Eliot Falls... the whole lot!

Wanna get the same Snatch Gear Shauno and Jock wear? Head to: https://snatchclothing.com.au/

Shauno's running the tough as nails Goodyear Wrangler Duratrac ATs - learn more: https://www.goodyear.com.au/

Sparesbox is the home of spares and accessories: https://www.sparesbox.com.au/

Check out Drifta roof top tents here: https://www.drifta.com.au/

Get the same suspension Shauno trusts in the Dirty 30: https://fulcrumsuspensions.com.au/

Shauno is running Teralume Icon driving lights - find them here: https://www.teralumeindustries.com/

Shaun & Graham rely on Nebo head torches and spotlights at night at camp - you can find them here: https://nebotools.com.au/

Shaun trusts Castrol oils in all his 4WDs. Learn More: https://rego2oil.castrol.com/en_au/au...

#4wd247 #4wd #capeyork #oldtelegraphtrack

snippet.title: The life of purple rice, pumpkins, and … peanuts紫米南瓜的一生…，还有花生丨Liziqi Channel
snippet.description:
Please  subscribe to 【李子柒 Liziqi 】Liziqi Channel on YouTube if you like my videos: https://goo.gl/nkjpSx 
Sow in spring to grow in summer, harvest in autumn for storage in winter.
And Autumn Equinox has given way to Cold Dew now.
We have finished reaping the corn, grain, pumpkins, and peanuts,
ready to await the frost and snow in winter.
For the past Mid-Autumn Day, my cousin and cousin-in-law came back to spend the festival with granny.
Chitter-chatter, lively and jolly--that’s how festivals should be!
春生夏长，秋收冬藏。
秋分已去寒露来。
忙完玉米 谷子 南瓜 花生的收获存储之后
就该等着霜雪天的到来，
中秋，表姐和表姐夫两口子来陪奶奶过节。
吵吵闹闹的，倒也过了这个秋！

snippet.title: Inside the Lincoln Project's campaign against President Trump
snippet.description:
A group of longtime Republican strategists who have worked with the likes of John McCain and George W. Bush have launched a scorching campaign against the president. Lesley Stahl reports.

Subscribe to the 60 Minutes Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/1S7CLRu
Watch Full Episodes of 60 Minutes HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Qkjo1F
Get more 60 Minutes from 60 Minutes: Overtime HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1KG3sdr
Relive past episodes and interviews with 60 Minutes Rewind HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1PlZiGI
Follow 60 Minutes on Instagram HERE: http://bit.ly/23Xv8Ry
Like 60 Minutes on Facebook HERE: http://on.fb.me/1Xb1Dao
Follow 60 Minutes on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1KxUsqX

Get the latest news and best in original reporting from CBS News delivered to your inbox. Subscribe to newsletters HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1RqHw7T

Get your news on the go! Download CBS News mobile apps HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Xb1WC8

Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: How Chefs In The NBA Bubble Make 4,000 Meals A Week | Big Business
snippet.description:
Alexia Grant, aka Chef Lex, was one of 10 chefs invited to cook for players inside the NBA bubble. From her kitchen at Disney World, she launched the pop-up restaurant Comfort Kitchen, specializing in Caribbean and Southern comfort food. Since, she's cooked for players from every team in the bubble, including the Miami Heat, the LA Lakers, and the Denver Nuggets. But cooking under strict quarantine isn't easy. She can't leave the bubble to do her own shopping and has to rely on runners to deliver her food to the players in the inner bubble.

snippet.description:

Late Night with Seth Meyers is supporting God’s Love We Deliver to help those in need during the COVID-19 pandemic. God’s Love We Deliver is a New York City-based organization that for over 30 years has provided personalized meals and nutrition counseling, free of charge, to those living with severe illnesses. With the help of 17,000 volunteers, God’s Love We Deliver provides over 2 million free meals each year to thousands of New York’s most vulnerable. snippet.title: When Time Became History - The Human Era
snippet.description:
** UPDATE: Calendars are sold out on the US-Shop but you can still get them from the EU-shop: https://shop-eu.kurzgesagt.org/ **

For the fifth time, we present to you the Human Era Calendar for the year 12,021 – this time it is all about the journey of humanity, beginning tens of thousands of years ago, leading into the revolution of agriculture, to ancient high civilizations and the beginning of modern times, culminating in a vision for our future. You can get the limited Edition now until we sell out and then never again. As always the calendar features 12 illustrated pages printed on high quality paper in Europe and the US. And this year the cover is especially shiny. The calendar will look great on your wall and let you dream about a glorious future. We truly have come far as a species! 

Sources & further reading:
https://sites.google.com/view/sourceswhentimebecamehistory

snippet.title: Epic Modern All Black Tiny House
snippet.description:
If you're a fan of ultra modern and minimalist design, then no doubt you're going to fall in love with this tiny house! The all black, trapezoidal exterior is absolutely striking, and the interior is spacious, well laid out and wonderfully designed to make a comfortable home. 

Jason and Sarah were drawn to the idea of living in a tiny house out of a desire to simplify their lives and focus on travel, sports and adventure. This off-the-grid tiny house gives them a beautiful, safe, secure and affordable place to call home which enables them to dedicate more time and resources to be able to do more of the things they love. 

We hope you enjoy the full tour of this very impressive off-the-grid tiny house.  

You can follow Jason and Sarah's adventures on Instagram:
Jason: https://www.instagram.com/jason_greenwood_nz/
Sarah: https://www.instagram.com/missscubainternationalnz2018/

Find out more about this tiny house and others on our website: https://www.livingbiginatinyhouse.com/epic-modern-all-black-tiny-house/

Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/livingbiginatinyhouse/

Follow us on Facebook:  http://www.facebook.com/livingbiginatinyhouse/

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/tinyhousenz

Please subscribe for more videos on tiny houses, architecture, DIY, design, and sustainable, off-grid living.

Title music in this video by Bryce Langston: http://www.youtube.com/brycelangston

Presented and Produced by: Bryce Langston
Camera: Rasa Pescud & Bryce Langston
Editing: Rasa Pescud & Archmage Cappuccino 

'Living Big in a Tiny House' © 2020 Zyia Pictures Ltd

snippet.title: iPHONE 12, 12 MINI, 12 PRO, 12 PRO MAX com 5G e HOMEPOD MINI! VEM CONFERIR os LANÇAMENTOS da APPLE!
snippet.description:
🚨🚨 LINKS das PROMOÇÕES do PRIME DAY abaixo 🚨🚨
💰Teste GRÁTIS o AMAZON PRIME por 30 DIAS: https://amzn.to/31lqel6
🎥 Assine o PRIME VIDEO no link: https://amzn.to/31lqel6

✌️ Me siga nas redes sociais:
https://www.instagram.com/matheuskise
https://www.twitter.com/matheuskise

🔠 Dispositivos Amazon (Até 40% off em dispositivos Echo e R$100 off no Kindle Paperwhite)
🔝 Kindle Paperwhite - De R$ 499 por R$ 399: https://amzn.to/34QIq91
🔝 Dispositivos Echo: https://amzn.to/3j1NqNr

🔠 Outras ofertas em serviços da Amazon
🔝 Amazon Music Unlimited: 4 meses por apenas R$ 1,99: https://amzn.to/3dqdXCD (Válido somente para Membros Prime que ainda não experimentaram o serviço de música)
🔝 Kindle Unlimited: https://amzn.to/3nLFeUQ (2 meses de Kindle Unlimited grátis equivalente a um desconto de R$ 19,90 ao mês, com acesso a mais de  1 milhão de ebooks para você ler onde e quando quiser.)

📚 Livros
🔝 Até 60% off em livros best-sellers: https://amzn.to/3jS2a2A

Qualquer um pode antecipar as compras de fim de ano com descontos neste Prime Day ao fazer parte do programa Amazon Prime.  Com apenas uma assinatura, o Amazon Prime oferece diversos benefícios como frete grátis e rápido em produtos elegíveis sem valor mínimo de compras para todo o Brasil , acesso a filmes e séries, música, livros e jogos, por apenas R$ 9,90/mês (ou a possibilidade de economizar 25% por R$89,00/ano).  Novos clientes podem experimentar Amazon Prime gratuitamente por 30 dias em https://amzn.to/2FmUuWT e se beneficiarem das ofertas exclusivas.

O primeiro modelo anunciado foi o iPhone 12 “comum” tela OLED SUPER RETINA XDR de 6,1 polegadas. Essa tela tem brilho aprimorado e um maior suporte ao HDR…
(Entre outras características, vemos as laterais quadradas de alumínio, e a parte traseira de vidro, o que permite o carregamento sem fio… Foi mencionado também uma proteção contra riscos aprimorada, o chamado Ceramic Shield e ele é até 4X mais resistente que as telas antigas…
Vale falar também que esse aparelho é 11% mais fino e 16% mais leve que o iPhone 11, bem bacana! E dentro dele está equipado o novo chip próprio da Apple, o A14, nem preciso comentar sobre perfomance… É um “processador” de 5 nanômetros, 40% mais veloz que o A13 (q já é fantástico) e tem como grande novidade uma melhor eficiência energética, ou seja, GERENCIAR BATERIA, ter uma autonomia daora!!! Vamos aguardar os testes… em breve aqui no canal!

Sobre as câmeras: segue basicamente a mesma coisa do iPhone 11, uma grande-angular de 12MP, f/2.4, e uma ‘principal'tambem de 12MP, f/1.6… Ou seja, a Apple lançou alguns incrementos na abertura, o que nos dá fotos 25% melhores em condições de baixa luz explicando de forma mais direta e descomplicada...
Também foi dito no evento que a empresa lançou melhorias nos modos Nodurno e HDR… mas ai só testando pra saber como é que é de verdade! Claro que mostraram várias fotos boas, até porque os iPhones são mt bons, isso ninguém pode negar!

Outra NOVIDADE bem legal foi o NOVO SISTEMA DE CARREGAMENTO SEM FIO dos iPhones!
É na verdade a volta do MagSafe (quem tem MacBooks mais antigos já conhecem)
O novo sistema que acompanha os iPhones faz o uso de ímãs. E traz suporte a até 15W (o que até dá pra considerar rapidinho, vai…” 
MAAAS não se deixe enganar, esses são ACESSÓRIOS a parte! Até pq os novos iPhones só virão com CABO mesmo, o adaptador de tomada foi REMOVIDO!
E eu falei acessórios, pq temos apenas o MagSafe e também o MagSafe Duo (que é capaz de carregar o iPhone e Apple Watch ao mesmo tempo)

Outro lançamento foi o iPhone 12 Mini, que basicamente é uma versão menor do iPhone 12 comum… Ele é bem compacto, traz uma tela de 5,4” e a Apple não deixou passar e reforçou que esse é o menor smartphone 5G do mundo.

Preços dos dispositivos: 699 dólares para a versão MINI e 799 para a versão COMUM nos Estados Unidos! Aqui no Brasil ainda não temos preços oficiais, tampouco data de chegada… mas obviamente virão beeeem caros!!

E agora vamos falar sobre os MODELOS PRO!
Também confirmando os rumores, esse segmento ganhou a nova cor azul, também presente nos Apple Watches Series 6! E tão bem bonitos!!
Traz três câmeras traseira + o sensor Lidar (já conhecido do iPad Pro de 2020)…
Além do azul, esses modelos virão em mais 3 cores, que são preto grafite, prata e dourado.

O modelo PRO “comum” salta de 5,8 para 6,1 polegadas. (Mesmo tamanho do iPhone 12 normal) e conta com os mesmos incrementos de maior resistência, etc…
A apple também citou que o recurso Deep Fusion foi melhorado e agora está presente até na câmera frontal, e junto do novo chip A14, elas ficam ainda melhores…

Falando em câmeras, o conjunto segue o mesmo do 11 Pro (uma principal, uma ultra angular e outra telefoto zoom, porém com MUDANÇAS)
O Pro terá 4x zoom; e o Pro Max terá 5x, um pouquinho melhor… Falando em Pro Max, ele também aumentou a tela, salta de 6,5 para 6,7 polegadas, também confirmando o que os rumores já diziam…

snippet.localized.title: iPHONE 12, 12 MINI, 12 PRO, 12 PRO MAX com 5G e HOMEPOD MINI! VEM CONFERIR os LANÇAMENTOS da APPLE!
snippet.localized.description:
🚨🚨 LINKS das PROMOÇÕES do PRIME DAY abaixo 🚨🚨
💰Teste GRÁTIS o AMAZON PRIME por 30 DIAS: https://amzn.to/31lqel6
🎥 Assine o PRIME VIDEO no link: https://amzn.to/31lqel6

✌️ Me siga nas redes sociais:
https://www.instagram.com/matheuskise
https://www.twitter.com/matheuskise

🔠 Dispositivos Amazon (Até 40% off em dispositivos Echo e R$100 off no Kindle Paperwhite)
🔝 Kindle Paperwhite - De R$ 499 por R$ 399: https://amzn.to/34QIq91
🔝 Dispositivos Echo: https://amzn.to/3j1NqNr

🔠 Outras ofertas em serviços da Amazon
🔝 Amazon Music Unlimited: 4 meses por apenas R$ 1,99: https://amzn.to/3dqdXCD (Válido somente para Membros Prime que ainda não experimentaram o serviço de música)
🔝 Kindle Unlimited: https://amzn.to/3nLFeUQ (2 meses de Kindle Unlimited grátis equivalente a um desconto de R$ 19,90 ao mês, com acesso a mais de  1 milhão de ebooks para você ler onde e quando quiser.)

📚 Livros
🔝 Até 60% off em livros best-sellers: https://amzn.to/3jS2a2A

Qualquer um pode antecipar as compras de fim de ano com descontos neste Prime Day ao fazer parte do programa Amazon Prime.  Com apenas uma assinatura, o Amazon Prime oferece diversos benefícios como frete grátis e rápido em produtos elegíveis sem valor mínimo de compras para todo o Brasil , acesso a filmes e séries, música, livros e jogos, por apenas R$ 9,90/mês (ou a possibilidade de economizar 25% por R$89,00/ano).  Novos clientes podem experimentar Amazon Prime gratuitamente por 30 dias em https://amzn.to/2FmUuWT e se beneficiarem das ofertas exclusivas.

O primeiro modelo anunciado foi o iPhone 12 “comum” tela OLED SUPER RETINA XDR de 6,1 polegadas. Essa tela tem brilho aprimorado e um maior suporte ao HDR…
(Entre outras características, vemos as laterais quadradas de alumínio, e a parte traseira de vidro, o que permite o carregamento sem fio… Foi mencionado também uma proteção contra riscos aprimorada, o chamado Ceramic Shield e ele é até 4X mais resistente que as telas antigas…
Vale falar também que esse aparelho é 11% mais fino e 16% mais leve que o iPhone 11, bem bacana! E dentro dele está equipado o novo chip próprio da Apple, o A14, nem preciso comentar sobre perfomance… É um “processador” de 5 nanômetros, 40% mais veloz que o A13 (q já é fantástico) e tem como grande novidade uma melhor eficiência energética, ou seja, GERENCIAR BATERIA, ter uma autonomia daora!!! Vamos aguardar os testes… em breve aqui no canal!

Sobre as câmeras: segue basicamente a mesma coisa do iPhone 11, uma grande-angular de 12MP, f/2.4, e uma ‘principal'tambem de 12MP, f/1.6… Ou seja, a Apple lançou alguns incrementos na abertura, o que nos dá fotos 25% melhores em condições de baixa luz explicando de forma mais direta e descomplicada...
Também foi dito no evento que a empresa lançou melhorias nos modos Nodurno e HDR… mas ai só testando pra saber como é que é de verdade! Claro que mostraram várias fotos boas, até porque os iPhones são mt bons, isso ninguém pode negar!

Outra NOVIDADE bem legal foi o NOVO SISTEMA DE CARREGAMENTO SEM FIO dos iPhones!
É na verdade a volta do MagSafe (quem tem MacBooks mais antigos já conhecem)
O novo sistema que acompanha os iPhones faz o uso de ímãs. E traz suporte a até 15W (o que até dá pra considerar rapidinho, vai…” 
MAAAS não se deixe enganar, esses são ACESSÓRIOS a parte! Até pq os novos iPhones só virão com CABO mesmo, o adaptador de tomada foi REMOVIDO!
E eu falei acessórios, pq temos apenas o MagSafe e também o MagSafe Duo (que é capaz de carregar o iPhone e Apple Watch ao mesmo tempo)

Outro lançamento foi o iPhone 12 Mini, que basicamente é uma versão menor do iPhone 12 comum… Ele é bem compacto, traz uma tela de 5,4” e a Apple não deixou passar e reforçou que esse é o menor smartphone 5G do mundo.

Preços dos dispositivos: 699 dólares para a versão MINI e 799 para a versão COMUM nos Estados Unidos! Aqui no Brasil ainda não temos preços oficiais, tampouco data de chegada… mas obviamente virão beeeem caros!!

E agora vamos falar sobre os MODELOS PRO!
Também confirmando os rumores, esse segmento ganhou a nova cor azul, também presente nos Apple Watches Series 6! E tão bem bonitos!!
Traz três câmeras traseira + o sensor Lidar (já conhecido do iPad Pro de 2020)…
Além do azul, esses modelos virão em mais 3 cores, que são preto grafite, prata e dourado.

O modelo PRO “comum” salta de 5,8 para 6,1 polegadas. (Mesmo tamanho do iPhone 12 normal) e conta com os mesmos incrementos de maior resistência, etc…
A apple também citou que o recurso Deep Fusion foi melhorado e agora está presente até na câmera frontal, e junto do novo chip A14, elas ficam ainda melhores…

Falando em câmeras, o conjunto segue o mesmo do 11 Pro (uma principal, uma ultra angular e outra telefoto zoom, porém com MUDANÇAS)
O Pro terá 4x zoom; e o Pro Max terá 5x, um pouquinho melhor… Falando em Pro Max, ele também aumentou a tela, salta de 6,5 para 6,7 polegadas, também confirmando o que os rumores já diziam… 
Recursos que merecem destaque: os iPhone’s 12 agora tiram fotos em RAW!

snippet.title: This is iPhone 12 Pro — Apple
snippet.description:
5G. A14 Bionic, the fastest chip in a smartphone. An all-new design. A Ceramic Shield front cover that’s tougher than any smartphone glass. A custom LiDAR Scanner. The first camera ever to record in Dolby Vision. An advanced Pro camera system for next-level low-light photography. And connect accessories in a whole new way with MagSafe. iPhone 12 Pro, the most powerful iPhone ever. 

Learn more: http://apple.com/iphone-12-pro

“Tomato Soup” by Hark Madley http://apple.co/TomatoSoup

 iPhone 12 Pro Max has not been authorized as required by the rules of the Federal Communications Commission. This device is not, and may not be, offered for sale or lease, or sold or leased, until authorization is obtained.

snippet.title: Moonlight - Alee | CHRIS | JayA Luuck (Mixtape ''Jovens Pretos Milionários'')
snippet.description:
Uma Realização Pineapple Storm Records.

“MOONLIGHT” é a primeira faixa da Mixtape “Jovens Pretos Milionários”, uma colab entre a Pineapple e a Hash Produções(BA).
São 6 faixas com videoclipe, JOVEM DEX e ALEE representando a Hash e CHRIS e JAYA LUUCK representando a Pineapple, participações especiais de Xamã e Borges.

Próximo lançamento dia 19/10 - CABUM - JayA Luuck e Jovem Dex

snippet.title: ♫ TALARICA - ESSES CRAQUES ESQUECERAM COMO JOGAR? I Paródia Rennan da Penha, MC 2jhow
snippet.description:
Uma paródia de futebol da música "Talarica" do Rennan da Penha e MC 2jhow. Esses caras já foram referências um dia desses, mas hoje tão em baixa, em má fase. Será que ainda tem jeito? Luan, Griezmann, Dembele, Hazard, Bale e vários outros, só as lendas que hoje em dia não tão jogando mais tanta bola! O que acontece com eles?

snippet.title: Modelo apontada como pivô da separação de Gusttavo Lima rebate acusação
snippet.description:
O fim do casamento de Gusttavo Lima e Andressa Suita está dando o que falar. A influencer Huma Kimak foi apontada como pivô da separação e rebateu as acusações em vídeo exclusivo enviado ao "A Tarde é Sua".



"Confesso que estou surpresa de estar aqui, nunca pensei que um boato sem pé nem cabeça pudesse ter esse tipo de proporção. Queria esclarecer que eu e Gusttavo nunca tivemos nenhum tipo de contato, nem de fã porque sou fã dele", disse Huma Kimak.



A influencer também contou que recebe diversos ataques na internet desde a época em que foi contratada para fazer a divulgação de uma live do Gusttavo Lima em Manaus, capital do Amazonas.



"Fui até o local onde seria o show, divulguei e no dia seguinte foi feita a live que eu não pude ir, porque estava me sentindo mal", explicou Huma.



A notícia da separação de Gusttavo Lima e Andressa Suita foi divulgada no dia 9 de outubro. A relação chegou ao fim após cinco anos e houve rumores de uma suposta traição do cantor. #ATardeESua

snippet.title: Apex Legends Champion Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Make your name with the Champion Edition, packed full of character unlocks and exclusive items to get you started right. http://x.ea.com/65702

Ready to become an Apex Champion? You could be, with all the incredible items stuffed into the Champion Edition. You’ll get every Legend up to Season 7, plus over $100 worth of exclusive cosmetics, including Legendary character and weapon skins and a Legendary gun charm, along with a thousand Apex Coins. Play who you want, dress how you want, and show those other Legends there’s a new champ in town. 

Starting Season 7, you can find the Champion Edition on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and Origin on PC or get a download card at your favorite retailer soon for $39.99. Here’s everything you’ll find inside:

The Champion Edition
- 9 character unlocks (all Legends up to Season 7):
Caustic, Mirage, Octane, Wattson, Crypto, Revenant, Loba, Rampart, and the Season 7 Legend 
- 7 Exclusive Legendary items:
- “Risen Queen” Wraith skin
- “Forged Knight” Revenant skin
- “Hallowed Spirit” Crypto skin
- “Curse of the Awaken” Triple Take skin
- “Slayer’s Lancer” Flatline skin
- “Jaded Myth” Sentinel skin
- "Emperor Nessy XIV" Gun Charm
- 1,000 Apex Coins

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC. 

Learn more about Apex Legends Season 6 – Boosted: http://x.ea.com/64060
 
Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

#PlayApex #ApexSeason6 #ChampionEdition #ApexLegends

Er du klar til at blive Apex-mester? Det kan du blive med alle de fantastiske genstande, som Champion Edition indeholder. Med sæson 7 kan du finde Champion Edition på Xbox One, PlayStation 4 og Origin til pc eller som download-kort hos din foretrukne forhandler for 39,99 $. Her er en oversigt over indholdet:

Champion Edition
●        9 oplåste legender (alle legender frem til sæson 7):

localizations.ru.description:
Заявите о себе с помощью издания чемпиона, которое включает кучу персонажей и эксклюзивных предметов. http://x.ea.com/65702

Готовы стать чемпионом Apex? Это вполне возможно. А предметы из издания чемпиона помогут вам заявить о себе. Вы получите всех легенд, выпущенных до 7-го сезона, а также эксклюзивные предметы внешнего вида на сумму более 100 $, включая легендарные облики и раскраски и легендарный талисман для оружия, а также 1000 монет Apex. Играйте за кого хотите, одевайтесь, как хотите, и покажите другим легендам, что к ним пожаловал новый чемпион. 

Начиная с 7-го сезона, издание чемпиона будет доступно на Xbox One, PlayStation 4 и в Origin для ПК, а скоро появится и на картах загрузки в вашем любимом розничном магазине за 39,99 $. Вот что вы в нем найдете:

○        Облик Ревенанта «Кованый рыцарь»

localizations.ja.title: エーペックスレジェンズ チャンピオンエディション トレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
チャンピオンエディションで君の名を轟かせよう。全キャラクターがアンロックされ、限定アイテムを今すぐ装備してバトルに参戦可能だ。http://x.ea.com/65702

Apexチャンピオンを目指そう！チャンピオンエディションに収録される豪華アイテムを手にすれば、チャンピオンも夢ではない。シーズン7までの全レジェンドがアンロック。加えて、100ドル相当の限定装飾アイテムも収録される。レジェンダリーのキャラクタースキンや武器スキン、レジェンダリーガンチャーム、そして1000 Apexコインも手に入る。好きなキャラクターを好きなアイテムで着飾り、他のレジェンドたちに新たなチャンピオンの到来を見せつけてやろう。

シーズン7開始と同時にXbox One、PlayStation®4、Origin（PC）版のチャンピオンエディションをご用意。販売店ではダウンロードカードもお買い求めいただけます。お値段は$39.99です。収録内容:

チャンピオンエディション
●        9人のキャラクターをアンロック（シーズン7までの全キャラクター）:
○        コースティック、ミラージュ、オクタン、ワットソン、クリプト、レヴナント、ローバ、ランパート、シーズン7のレジェンド
●        限定レジェンダリーアイテム7種:
○        レイス用スキン「昇日の女王」
○        レヴナント用スキン「人造の騎士」
○        クリプト用スキン「神聖なる魂」
○        トリプルテイク用スキン「覚醒の呪い」
○        フラットライン用スキン「スレイヤーズランサー」
○        センチネル用スキン「退屈な神話」
○        ガンチャーム「皇帝ネッシーXIV」
●        1,000 Apexコイン

「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は、伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う、基本プレイ無料のバトルロイヤル作品。Xbox One、PS4、Origin（PC）で今すぐ無料プレイ。

snippet.title: Unsere traumhafte Hausgeburt ❤️ Überraschungs-Baby | Isabeau
snippet.description:
Hi Zusammen, wir durften eine wunderschöne Hausgeburt erleben. Zudem haben wir uns bei dem Geschlecht bis zur Geburt überraschen lassen. Ich wünsche euch viel Spaß bei diesem emotionalen Video. 

Kanal Mitglied werden: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCucHkPnBa7pB-jITCGuSqKw/join

Ich würde mich mega über einen Daumen nach oben freuen & lasst mir gerne euer Feedback da! ♥

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

WERBUNG:
MEIN ONLINE SHOP: http://www.isabeau-shop.de 
MEIN MAMI BUCH | Isi durch die Schwangerschaft:
https://www.thalia.de/shop/home/artikeldetails/isi_durch_die_schwangerschaft/isabeau/ISBN3-96096-022-0/ID64513624.html 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

♥ Soziale Netzwerke:
Instagram: isabeau_youtube

E-Mail Kontakt für Firmen und Werbekunden:
isabeau-youtube@gmx.de

♥ Häufig gestellte Fragen von Euch:

Mit welcher Kamera drehst du deine Videos?
- Olympus OM-D E-M5 II
Welches Objektiv benutzt du?
- Sigma 30 mm F1,4
Welches Videobearbeitungsprogramm verwendest du?
- Final Cut Pro X oder iMovie
Wie bist du dazu gekommen, Youtube Videos zu machen?
- Langeweile in der Schwangerschaft :)
Wie alt seid Ihr?
- Isabeau: 22.06.1991 | Alex: 24.10.1987 | Leona: 26.04.2012 | Pauline: 7.05.2016 | Frida: 13.09.2017
Seid Alex & Du verheiratet? 
- Ja seit dem 18.02.2017
Wieso zeigt ihr eure Kinder nicht? 
- Um sie zu schützen und ihre Privatsphäre zu bewahren. Zudem sollen unsere Kinder später selbst entscheiden, ob sie im Internet zu sehen sein wollen oder nicht! :)
Heißt du wirklich "Isabeau"?
- Ja mein Name ist Isabeau und wird Isabo ausgesprochen. Der Name kommt aus Frankreich und bedeutet so viel wie: Isa die Schöne
Was sind eure Berufe?
- Ich bin gelernte Krankenschwester. Alex arbeitet als Elektriker für Automatisierungstechnik.

DANKE FÜR EURE UNTERSTÜTZUNG! 

Ich wünsche Euch viel Spaß auf meinem Kanal:)
Verpasst keine Videos und abonniert mich, ist kostenlos!

Fühlt Euch gedrückt, eure Isabeau ♥

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Hackentor rettet DFB-Team einen Punkt: Deutschland - Schweiz 3:3 | UEFA Nations League | DAZN
snippet.description:
Nach dem ersten Sieg in der Nations League gegen die Ukraine, empfängt die deutsche Nationalmannschaft nun die Schweiz. Doch der Start geht zunächst richtig schief, nachdem die Eidgenossen durch Tore von Gavranovic und Freuler in Führung gehen. Timo Werner erzielt den Anschlusstreffer, womit es mit einem 1:2 in die Pause geht. Kai Havertz trifft nach dem Seitenwechsel zum zwischenzeitlichen Ausgleich. Doch erneut schlägt Gavranovic zu, und bringt die Gäste in Führung. Serge Gnabry rettet dem DFB-Team am Ende allerdings durch einen sehenswerten Hackentreffer einen Punkt, womit das deutsche Team in der Nations League weiterhin ungeschlagen bleibt. Die Schweiz wartet dagegen noch auf ihren ersten Sieg.

snippet.title: Lawinenunglück: Fabiana verliert ihren Verlobten kurz vor der Hochzeit I TRU DOKU
snippet.description:
TRU DOKU über Fabiana (32). Kurz vor der Hochzeit erreicht sie die schreckliche Nachricht: Ihr Verlobter wurde von einer Lawine erfasst. Wie geht sie mit diesem schmerzvollen Verlust um? 


🟡 🔔 TRU DOKU jetzt abonnieren: http://bit.ly/TRUDOKUABO

 
#lostmylove #trudoku #funk

Stell dir vor, du verlierst die Liebe deines Lebens! Fabiana freut sich unglaublich auf ihre baldige Hochzeit mit ihrem Verlobten Daniel. Für sie ist die Beziehung der beiden absolut perfekt. Doch dann bricht von heute auf morgen Fabianas Welt zusammen: Kurz vor der Hochzeit stirbt ihr Verlobter bei einem Lawinenunglück. 
Daniel, ein begeisterter Skifahrer, macht sich im Januar 2019 mit drei Freunden auf nach Österreich, um dort Ski zu fahren und die Berge zu genießen. Doch irgendwann meldet er sich mehr bei Fabiana – sie macht sich Sorgen. Kurz darauf erfährt Fabiana: Es gab ein Lawinenunglück! Daniels Freunde werden noch in derselben Nacht tot geborgen. Nur von Daniel ist keine Spur! Nach zähen Tagen des Wartens und Hoffens bleibt Fabiana nichts anderes mehr übrig: Sie sagt schweren Herzens die Hochzeit ab. Vier Tage später die Gewissheit: Ihr Verlobter wird tot gefunden. Am Boden zerstört gibt Fabiana nicht auf. Sie kauft ein baufälliges Haus und renoviert Zimmer für Zimmer, um ihre Trauer zu bewältigen.

snippet.localized.title: Lawinenunglück: Fabiana verliert ihren Verlobten kurz vor der Hochzeit I TRU DOKU
snippet.localized.description:
TRU DOKU über Fabiana (32). Kurz vor der Hochzeit erreicht sie die schreckliche Nachricht: Ihr Verlobter wurde von einer Lawine erfasst. Wie geht sie mit diesem schmerzvollen Verlust um? 


🟡 🔔 TRU DOKU jetzt abonnieren: http://bit.ly/TRUDOKUABO

 
#lostmylove #trudoku #funk

Stell dir vor, du verlierst die Liebe deines Lebens! Fabiana freut sich unglaublich auf ihre baldige Hochzeit mit ihrem Verlobten Daniel. Für sie ist die Beziehung der beiden absolut perfekt. Doch dann bricht von heute auf morgen Fabianas Welt zusammen: Kurz vor der Hochzeit stirbt ihr Verlobter bei einem Lawinenunglück. 
Daniel, ein begeisterter Skifahrer, macht sich im Januar 2019 mit drei Freunden auf nach Österreich, um dort Ski zu fahren und die Berge zu genießen. Doch irgendwann meldet er sich mehr bei Fabiana – sie macht sich Sorgen. Kurz darauf erfährt Fabiana: Es gab ein Lawinenunglück! Daniels Freunde werden noch in derselben Nacht tot geborgen. Nur von Daniel ist keine Spur! Nach zähen Tagen des Wartens und Hoffens bleibt Fabiana nichts anderes mehr übrig: Sie sagt schweren Herzens die Hochzeit ab. Vier Tage später die Gewissheit: Ihr Verlobter wird tot gefunden. Am Boden zerstört gibt Fabiana nicht auf. Sie kauft ein baufälliges Haus und renoviert Zimmer für Zimmer, um ihre Trauer zu bewältigen.

snippet.title: Seltene Krankheit: Mein Leben ohne Heilung | Wie lebe ich mit einer schweren Krankheit? Folge 7
snippet.description:
Robin leidet seit seiner Geburt unter einer schweren Hautkrankheit in Verbindung mit Rheuma und einer Erkrankung der Leber – was genau das für eine Krankheit ist, wieso er sie hat und wie man diese heilen kann, weiß aber keiner. 

Seit Jahren versuchen seine Ärzt*innen herauszufinden, wieso Robin die seltene Krankheit bekommen hat – letztendlich ist sie aber noch viel zu unerforscht…

Für ihn ist die Hautkrankheit Teil seines Alltags. Mehrmals am Tag muss er sich eincremen, er kann nicht schwitzen und seine Augen sind konstant am Tränen und gerötet. Zudem wird er immer mit neugierigen Blicken von fremden Menschen auf der Straße konfrontiert – denn seine #Hautkrankheit ist sehr auffällig. 

Frank ist gemeinsam mit ihm zu Robins Ärztin gegangen und wollte wissen, wie Robin mit der seltenen Erkrankung umgeht und wieso er sich bei uns gemeldet hat, um im Film darüber zu sprechen. 

Folge 7 der Frage „Wie lebe ich mit einer schweren Krankheit?“ 

Hier geht’s zur Playlist mit allen Folgen: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y1SgLZsoGPA&list=PL2lvsm4ys5nF5VZZ9tV1xrk9PgFo13oml

Wenn ihr noch mehr über Frank erfahren wollt – hier geht es zu seinem Instagram-Account: https://www.instagram.com/f_cybert/

Reporter: Frank Seibert 
Autor*in: Sarah Sliwa  
Kamera: Markus Valley 
Schnitt: Markus Valley / Robert Stöger 
Channel Management: Samira Schütz 
Community Management: Kim Stoppert / Samira Schütz
Redaktion: Florian Meyer-Hawranek


Das ist #DieFrage: 

Es gibt diese großen, kniffligen Fragen, auf die es keine einfachen Antworten gibt: Warum mobben wir? Warum lassen wir Tiere leiden? Saufen wir zu viel? Oder: Was machen Pornos mit uns? 
Mein Team und mich interessieren Fragen, die direkt etwas mit unserem Leben zu tun haben, aber auch Themen, die uns allen wichtig sind und oft nur oberflächlich diskutiert werden. 
Wir suchen Antworten auf diese Fragen, Woche für Woche – offen, ehrlich und unabhängig. Dafür treffen wir keine Experten, sondern sind dabei: auf dem Schlachthof, auf der Swinger-Party, beim Missionieren in der Fußgängerzone. 
Und weil wir auf unserer Suche möglichst viele Perspektiven kennenlernen möchten, beschäftigt uns eine Frage immer mehrere Wochen. Am Ende wollen wir eine Antwort geben, auch wenn uns das nicht leichtfällt. 
Mit jedem Video – aber erst recht in den Diskussionen mit euch – kommen wir einer Antwort auf die großen, kniffligen Fragen aber ein Stück näher.

Die Frage auf Facebook: 
https://www.facebook.com/DieFrage/
Die Frage auf Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/diefrage_offiziell/

snippet.localized.title: Seltene Krankheit: Mein Leben ohne Heilung | Wie lebe ich mit einer schweren Krankheit? Folge 7
snippet.localized.description:
Robin leidet seit seiner Geburt unter einer schweren Hautkrankheit in Verbindung mit Rheuma und einer Erkrankung der Leber – was genau das für eine Krankheit ist, wieso er sie hat und wie man diese heilen kann, weiß aber keiner. 

Seit Jahren versuchen seine Ärzt*innen herauszufinden, wieso Robin die seltene Krankheit bekommen hat – letztendlich ist sie aber noch viel zu unerforscht…

Für ihn ist die Hautkrankheit Teil seines Alltags. Mehrmals am Tag muss er sich eincremen, er kann nicht schwitzen und seine Augen sind konstant am Tränen und gerötet. Zudem wird er immer mit neugierigen Blicken von fremden Menschen auf der Straße konfrontiert – denn seine #Hautkrankheit ist sehr auffällig. 

Frank ist gemeinsam mit ihm zu Robins Ärztin gegangen und wollte wissen, wie Robin mit der seltenen Erkrankung umgeht und wieso er sich bei uns gemeldet hat, um im Film darüber zu sprechen. 

Folge 7 der Frage „Wie lebe ich mit einer schweren Krankheit?“ 

Hier geht’s zur Playlist mit allen Folgen: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y1SgLZsoGPA&list=PL2lvsm4ys5nF5VZZ9tV1xrk9PgFo13oml

Wenn ihr noch mehr über Frank erfahren wollt – hier geht es zu seinem Instagram-Account: https://www.instagram.com/f_cybert/

Reporter: Frank Seibert 
Autor*in: Sarah Sliwa  
Kamera: Markus Valley 
Schnitt: Markus Valley / Robert Stöger 
Channel Management: Samira Schütz 
Community Management: Kim Stoppert / Samira Schütz
Redaktion: Florian Meyer-Hawranek


Das ist #DieFrage: 

Es gibt diese großen, kniffligen Fragen, auf die es keine einfachen Antworten gibt: Warum mobben wir? Warum lassen wir Tiere leiden? Saufen wir zu viel? Oder: Was machen Pornos mit uns? 
Mein Team und mich interessieren Fragen, die direkt etwas mit unserem Leben zu tun haben, aber auch Themen, die uns allen wichtig sind und oft nur oberflächlich diskutiert werden. 
Wir suchen Antworten auf diese Fragen, Woche für Woche – offen, ehrlich und unabhängig. Dafür treffen wir keine Experten, sondern sind dabei: auf dem Schlachthof, auf der Swinger-Party, beim Missionieren in der Fußgängerzone. 
Und weil wir auf unserer Suche möglichst viele Perspektiven kennenlernen möchten, beschäftigt uns eine Frage immer mehrere Wochen. Am Ende wollen wir eine Antwort geben, auch wenn uns das nicht leichtfällt. 
Mit jedem Video – aber erst recht in den Diskussionen mit euch – kommen wir einer Antwort auf die großen, kniffligen Fragen aber ein Stück näher.

Die Frage auf Facebook: 
https://www.facebook.com/DieFrage/
Die Frage auf Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/diefrage_offiziell/

snippet.title: Rick, die heimliche Affäre?! 🏳️‍🌈👨‍❤️‍👨💔😟  | Berlin - Tag & Nacht #2299
snippet.description:
Jan bittet Rick um ein Date. Der lässt sich darauf ein, obwohl Jade und Mandy dagegen sind! Rick ist total überrascht, als das Date mit Jan ziemlich gut läuft. Doch plötzlich taucht Jans Freund, der eine sichtbare Ablehnung gegen homosexueller Männer hat, auf. Wie wird er reagieren? Wird er zu Rick und dem Date stehen?

Die gescriptete Reality-Soap „Berlin - Tag & Nacht“ zeigt die coolste WG Berlins, mit Themen wie  Freundschaft, Liebe,  Eifersucht, Affären, Glück, Freude und Leiden. Wie im echten Leben eben!
Alte wie neue WG-Bewohner, u. a. Ole, Joe, Peggy, Krätze, Schmidti, Eule, Basti Paula, Piet, Milla, Leon und viele weitere, zeigen dir ihr Leben in Berlin, der bunten Metropole Deutschlands. Sie nehmen dich mit in ihre Wohngemeinschaften, auf ihre Arbeitsplätze, in den Club Matrix, den Friseursalon „Schnitte“ sowie die Bar LA 14. Auch ein Tattoostudio und das Fitnessstudio Body Burn gehören zu den unterschiedlichen und wechselnden Handlungsorten der Serie. Die Großstadt-Soap „Berlin – Tag & Nacht“ ist nicht zuletzt deshalb so beliebt, weil sie die Bewohner der WGs im Ringen mit alltäglichen Problemen zeigt: Affäre und Eifersucht, Erfolgsdruck im Beruf sowie viele zwischenmenschliche Konflikte. 

"Berlin - Tag & Nacht" läuft Montag bis Freitag um 19:05 Uhr bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.title: schnelles und einfaches Rezept für Nudeln zum Abendessen, Nudeln in einer Pfanne kochen #157
snippet.description:
schnelles und einfaches Nudelrezept zum Abendessen, Nudeln in einer Pfanne zuzubereiten ist ein schnelles Rezept für jeden Tag. Ein einfaches Rezept für das Abendessen, das sowohl dem Koch als auch der ganzen Familie gefällt. Sie müssen Nudeln nicht mehr separat kochen. Leckeres Pastarezept, perfekt für ein schnelles Abendessen.
Kochrezept und Zutaten:
1 Zwiebel hacken
1 Karotte reiben
Zwiebeln und Karotten ein paar Minuten braten *
2 Hähnchenfilets in Würfel geschnitten
Das Filet einige Minuten braten
fügen Sie 4 Esslöffel Tomatensauce oder 2 Esslöffel Tomatenmark hinzu
Salz, Pfeffer, gemahlener Paprika und provenzalische Kräuter
7 Minuten bei schwacher Hitze kochen lassen
300 g Nudeln und 500 ml Wasser hinzufügen
Bei mittlerer Hitze abgedeckt bis zu 10 Minuten kochen lassen
Das Ergebnis ist einfach super
Guten Appetit
ein paar Minuten sind es bis zu 5 Minuten

localizations.en.title: quick and easy recipe for pasta for dinner, cook pasta in a pan # 157
localizations.en.description:
quick and easy pasta recipe for dinner, making pasta in a pan is a quick recipe for every day. A simple dinner recipe that will delight both the cook and the whole family. You no longer have to cook pasta separately. Delicious pasta recipe, perfect for a quick dinner.
Cooking recipe and ingredients:
Chop 1 onion
Grate 1 carrot
Fry the onions and carrots for a few minutes *
2 chicken fillets cut into cubes
Fry the fillet for a few minutes
add 4 tablespoons of tomato sauce or 2 tablespoons of tomato paste
Salt, pepper, ground paprika and Provencal herbs
Cook for 7 minutes over low heat
Add 300 g of pasta and 500 ml of water
Cover and cook over medium heat for up to 10 minutes
The result is just great
Good Appetite
a few minutes up to 5 minutes

Hak 1 løg
Riv 1 gulerod
Steg løg og gulerødder i et par minutter *

Steg fileten i et par minutter

Trita 1 cipolla
Grattugia 1 carota

Friggere il filetto per qualche minuto

Aggiungere 300 g di pasta e 500 ml di acqua

Il risultato è semplicemente fantastico

localizations.ga.description:
oideas pasta tapa agus éasca don dinnéar, is oideas tapa laethúil é pasta a dhéanamh i bpanna. Oideas dinnéar simplí a thaitneoidh leis an gcócaire agus leis an teaghlach ar fad. Ní gá duit pasta a chócaráil ar leithligh a thuilleadh. Oideas pasta blasta, foirfe do dhinnéar gasta.
Oideas cócaireachta agus comhábhair:
Gearr 1 oinniún
Gráta 1 cairéad
Fry na oinniúin agus na cairéid ar feadh cúpla nóiméad *
2 filléad sicín gearrtha i gciúbanna
Fry an filléad ar feadh cúpla nóiméad
cuir 4 spúnóg bhoird de anlann trátaí nó 2 spúnóg bhoird de ghreamú trátaí leis
Salann, piobar, paprika talún agus luibheanna Provencal
Cócaráil ar feadh 7 nóiméad thar teas íseal
Cuir 300 g de pasta agus 500 ml uisce leis
Clúdaigh agus cócaráil thar mheán teasa ar feadh suas le 10 nóiméad
Is é an toradh ach iontach
Goile maith
cúpla nóiméad suas le 5 nóiméad

localizations.sl.title: hiter in enostaven recept za testenine za večerjo, skuhajte testenine v ponvi # 157
localizations.sl.description:
hiter in enostaven recept za testenine za večerjo, priprava testenin v ponvi je hiter recept za vsak dan. Preprost recept za večerjo, ki bo razveselil tako kuharja kot vso družino. Testenin vam ni več treba kuhati ločeno. Okusen recept za testenine, kot nalašč za hitro večerjo.
Kuharski recept in sestavine:
Sesekljajte 1 čebulo
Naribajte 1 korenček
Čebulo in korenje pražimo nekaj minut *
2 piščančja fileja narezana na kocke
File pražimo nekaj minut
dodajte 4 žlice paradižnikove omake ali 2 žlici paradižnikove paste
Sol, poper, mleta paprika in provansalska zelišča
Kuhajte 7 minut na majhnem ognju
Dodamo 300 g testenin in 500 ml vode
Pokrijemo in na zmernem ognju kuhamo do 10 minut
Rezultat je naravnost odličen
Dober tek
nekaj minut do 5 minut
Prijatelji, če vam je bil video všeč, lahko kanalu pomagate:
This Delite ta video s prijatelji v družabnih omrežjih. Network + recept bo shranjen na vašem spletnem mestu!
OCENITE VIDEO! 👍 - to je zame prijetno in pomembno za razvoj kanala!

localizations.cs.description:
rychlý a snadný recept na těstoviny k večeři, výroba těstovin na pánvi je rychlý každodenní recept. Jednoduchý recept na večeři, který potěší kuchaře i celou rodinu. Už nemusíte vařit těstoviny samostatně. Lahodný recept na těstoviny, ideální pro rychlou večeři.
Recept na vaření a přísady:
Nakrájejte 1 cibuli
Nastrouhejte 1 mrkev
Smažte cibuli a mrkev několik minut *
2 kuřecí filé nakrájené na kostky
Smažte filé několik minut
přidejte 4 lžíce rajčatové omáčky nebo 2 lžíce rajčatové pasty
Sůl, pepř, mletá paprika a provensálské bylinky
Vaříme 7 minut na mírném ohni
Přidejte 300 g těstovin a 500 ml vody
Zakryjte a vařte na středním ohni až 10 minut
Výsledek je prostě skvělý
Chuť k jídlu
několik minut až 5 minut

localizations.is.description:
fljótleg og auðveld pastauppskrift í kvöldmat, að búa til pasta á pönnu er fljótleg hversdagsuppskrift. Einföld kvöldmataruppskrift sem mun gleðja bæði matreiðslumanninn og alla fjölskylduna. Þú þarft ekki lengur að elda pasta sérstaklega. Ljúffeng pastauppskrift, fullkomin fyrir fljótlegan kvöldmat.
Matreiðsluuppskrift og innihaldsefni:
Saxið 1 lauk
Rifið 1 gulrót
Steikið laukinn og gulræturnar í nokkrar mínútur *
2 kjúklingaflök skorin í teninga
Steikið flakið í nokkrar mínútur
bætið við 4 msk af tómatsósu eða 2 msk af tómatmauki
Salt, pipar, möluð paprika og Provencal kryddjurtir
Eldið í 7 mínútur við vægan hita
Bætið við 300 g af pasta og 500 ml af vatni
Lokið og eldið við meðalhita í allt að 10 mínútur
Útkoman er bara frábær
Góð matarlyst
nokkrar mínútur upp í 5 mínútur

snippet.title: Die Mannschaft: 5 Gründe für den Absturz!
snippet.description:
Die Deutsche Nationalmannschaft liegt am Boden! Immer weniger Fans kommen in die Stadien, und immer weniger Leute sehen sich Länderspiele im Fernsehen an. Woran liegt das? Ich denke: 5 Gründe gibt's, weshalb das DFB-Team bzw. "Die Mannschaft" keinerlei Relevanz mehr besitzt. Gibt es unter Bundestrainer Jogi Löw überhaupt noch ein Leistungsprinzip? Weshalb dürfen Spieler wie Julian Draxler oder Antonio Rüdiger dauerhaft spielen? Geben die Nationalspieler wirklich 100%, wenn sie auf dem Platz stehen und den Adler des DFB-Teams auf der Brust tragen? Welche Werte vermittelt der DFB? Ist er wirklich in Sachen Klimaschutz und Rassismus im Jahr 2020 angekommen? Und: Wie sieht die sportliche Perspektive im Fußball aus? Spielt "Die Mannschaft" noch attraktiven Fußball, oder wo liegen die Probleme? Viele Dinge über den DFB werden angesprochen, viel Spaß bei der aktuellen Analyse. 

#DieMannschaft #DFB #NationsLeague
----
WICHTIG: Die Trikots, die in den Videos getragen werden, spiegeln nicht meine Sympathien wider. Es dient lediglich dazu, das aktuelle Thema zu untermalen.
